comments: Antetokounmpo (MIL) is deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Holiday (MIL) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt and any contact after his release is incidental.

Portis (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position and makes marginal contact to Thompson's (CHI) head. Contact to an opponent?s head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact initiated by LaVine (CHI) as the two players come together.
Dosunmu (CHI) makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) left arm that affects his shot near the rim.

Replay review of the foul called on Middleton (MIL) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Middleton makes marginal contact with LaVine's (CHI) body after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
MIL calls a timeout prior to Dosunmu (CHI) committing a take foul on Carter (MIL).
Dosunmu (CHI) commits a take foul on Holiday (MIL).
